Guidelime.registerGuide(
[[
[N49-50 Tanaris]
[GA Horde]
[D A guide created by T H A C E N#9446\Based on Joana's Speed Leveling guide https://www.joanasworld.com]
01) As you enter Gadgetzan (next to the crane, [G52,27Tanaris]), accept "[QA3362 Thistleshrub Valley]".
02) Behind the Inn, next to the Bonfire, accept "[QA5863 The Dunemaul Compound]" ([G53,27]).
03) Go in the Inn and make Gadgetzan your new home ([G52,28]).
04) Go to the Bank (SE in Gadgetzan, [G52,29]) and get the following items out: Yeh'kinya's Bramble, Goodsteel Ledger, 20 Solid Crystal Leg Shafts, Goodsteel's Balanced Flameberge, Wastewander Water Pouches and Hippogryph Egg. Put in the bank: your stack of Long Elegant Feathers (if you still need to turn in the quest for them)
05) Next to the Inn/Bank at the windmill ([G52,29]), turn in "[QT243 Into the Field]", accept and complete "[QT379 Slake That Thirst]". Do not accept the quest from the item received yet, this will be done later.
06) Go to the Egg-O-Matic machine in Gadgetzan (next to the teleporter, [G52,27]), and turn in your Hippogryph Egg for "[QT2741 The Super Egg-O-Matic]" quest (additional eggs do not yield XP). NOTE: You can turn in different types of eggs at the NPC next to the machine for a non-XP reward.
07) Next to the AH, accept "[QA2605 The Thirsty Goblin]" ([G52,29]).
08) Next to the Forge, turn in "[QT4450 Ledger from Tanaris]" ([G52,29]).
09) On the western side of Gadgetzan, up on the hill, accept "[QA82 Noxious Lair Investigation]" ([G50,28]).
10) Go south to the Broken Pillar and turn in "[QT3380 The Sunken Temple]" ([G53,46]), accept "[QA3444 The Stone Circle]". Also accept "[QA3161 Gahz'ridian]".
11) Go SW and do part of "[QC5863 The Dunemaul Compound]": kill Gor'marok the Ravager (in the small cave, [G41,58]).
12) Go south to Southmoon Ruins (around [G41,73]) and do "[QC5863 The Dunemaul Compound]" along with "[QC3161 Gahz'ridian]": kill Dunemaul Brutes and Dunemaul Enforcers. Also loot the Gahz'ridian from the ground. TIP: You can equip the Gahz'ridian Detector helm to help you see the Gahz'ridian on the minimap. Also, there is another area of mobs, but with less Gahz'ridian, (around [G47,65]).
13) Go west to The Noxious Lair (around [G34,47]) and do "[QC82 Noxious Lair Investigation]": kill/loot the Centipaar bugs, and any of them can drop the insect parts.
14) Go south to Thistleshrub Valley (around [G30,65]) and do "[QC3362 Thistleshrub Valley]" along with "[QC2605 The Thirsty Goblin]": kill 8 Gnarled Thistleshrubs and 8 Thistleshrub Rootshapers. Also kill/loot the Thistleshrub Dew Collectors /target for the Laden Dew Gland (low drop rate).
15) At the Thistleshrub Valley ([G32,74] or [G29,63]) accept and do the escort quest "[QC1560 Tooga's Quest]": escort Tooga /target (turtle) NE to Torta (At next step):
16) Once at Torta ([G66,25]), turn in "[QT1560 Tooga's Quest]".
17) Just north of you at Steamwheedle port, go in the southern hut and accept "[QA4324 Yuka Screwspigot]" ([G67,24]).
18) North at Steamwheedle Port turn in "[QT3520 Screecher Spirits]" ([G67,22]), SKIP "The Prophecy of Mosh'aru" (Zul'Farrak Dungeon). 
19) Hearth to Gadgetzan. Make sure you are repaired/resupplied.
20) Next to the AH ([G52,29]), turn in "[QT2605 The Thirsty Goblin]", accept "[QA2606 In Good Taste]".
21) At Sprinkle (NW hut, [G51,27]), turn in "[QT2606 In Good Taste]", accept "[QA2641 Sprinkle's Secret Ingredient]".
22) In the hut next to you, turn in "[QT82 Noxious Lair Investigation]" ([G51,27]).
23) Next to the crane near the Gadgetzan entrance, turn in "[QT3362 Thistleshrub Valley]" ([G52,27]).
24) Behind the Inn, next to the Bonfire, turn in "[QT5863 The Dunemaul Compound]" ([G53,27]).
25) Go to the Gadgetzan Bank (SE hut, [G52,29]) and get the following items out: Field Testing Kit and (if you have it) OOX-17/TN Distress Beacon.
26) On the western side of Gadgetzan, up on the hill, accept "[QA10 The Scrimshank Redemption]" ([G50,28]).
27) From the item Model 4711-FTZ Power Source in your inventory, accept and do "[QC654 Tanaris Field Sampling]": start killing beasts just south of Gadgetzan. You need to kill/loot any Basilisks, Hyenas, and Scorpids. You will find these beasts all around the open fields of Tanaris. As you get the untested samples, click them to get the acceptable ones. You only have 2 hours to do this and the next few steps, so work quickly. While doing this, do the following steps as well:
28) Grind your way down south to the Broken Pillar and turn in "[QT3161 Gahz'ridian]" ([G53,46]).
29) Grind east (to [G60,52]) and simply clear the mobs from this point to the next step's coordinates (to make the chicken escort quest easier):
30) If you have the item OOX-17/TN Distress Beacon, from it accept "[QA351 Find OOX-17/TN!]". Then turn this in (at [G60,65]) and accept and do the escort "[QC648 Rescue OOX-17/TN!]" It's important to try and keep aggro off of the Robot Chicken /target, as it can die easily. This escort leads all the way to Steamwheedle Port and takes roughly 21 minutes. If you have troubles with this quest, then it can be skipped.
31) Make sure "[QC654 Tanaris Field Sampling]" is complete. Then go SE to The Gaping Chasm and do "[QC10 The Scrimshank Redemption]": go in the specific cave (at [G56,69]) and keep making right turns in the cave, which will lead you to the item you need to loot.
32) Die on purpose to get back to Gadgetzan.
33) Next to the Inn at the windmill ([G52,29]), turn in "[QT654 Tanaris Field Sampling]", accept "[QA864 Return to Apothecary Zinge]". You can then destroy the Model 4711-FTZ Power Source item.
34) On the western side of Gadgetzan, up on the hill, turn in "[QT10 The Scrimshank Redemption]" ([G50,28]), accept "[QA110 Insect Part Analysis]".
35) In the hut NW in Gadgetzan, turn in "[QT110 Insect Part Analysis]", accept the next [QA113 part].
36) Go back to the western side of Gadgetzan, up on the hill ([G50,28], #8 on map) and turn in "[QT113 Insect Part Analysis]". Accept "[QA32 Rise of the Silithid]".
37) Make sure you are level 50, grind on any mob until you are.
38) Go to the Wind Rider Master (north of Gadgetzan, [G52,25]) and fly to Orgrimmar, Durotar.
39) Go in Orgrimmar's Inn and make it your new home ([G54,68]). And from the Innkeeper, accept "[QA936 Assisting Arch Druid Runetotem]". Make sure you are repaired/resupplied.
40) Go to the Bank ([G50,69]) and get the following items out: Box of Empty Vials and your stack of Long Elegant Feathers (if you still need to turn in the quest for them).
GET NEW ABILITIES) Get your level 50 spells/abilities. 
41) Go up to the Wind Rider Master ([G45,64]) and fly to Valormok, Azshara.
[NX 50-50 Azshara]
]], "Thacen")
